Flying, ward {2}
Curse of Deception — Whenever a player casts a spell targeting only one creature or player, roll a d6. On a 1 or 2, the creature that player controls with the highest power loses all abilities and becomes a 1/1 green Frog until end of turn. If tied for highest power, that player chooses one.
Whenever a creature becomes a Frog this way, you draw a card.

Ward {3}
At the beginning of your end step, if this creature wasn't dealt damage this turn, you draw a card and gain 2 life.
When this creature dies, exile it.
